OL,3,CDoctors in Wales urged to accept
OL,4,Clatest pay deal
OL,6,FA new pay offer has been put forward
OL,7,Fto doctors in Wales after months of
OL,8,Fnegotiations and strike action.
OL,10,FJunior doctors, specialist (SAS)
OL,11,Fdoctors and consultants are all now
OL,12,Fbeing encouraged by the union BMA
OL,13,FCymru Wales to accept the deal, with
OL,14,Fit being described as a 'big step in
OL,15,Fthe right direction'.
OL,17,FIt comes after strike action was put
OL,18,Fon pause in April for negotiations
OL,19,Fwith the Welsh Government.
