OL,3,CDoctors in Wales urged to accept
OL,4,Clatest pay deal
OL,6,FThree rounds saw 10 days of industrial
OL,7,Faction by junior doctors this year
OL,8,Fwith operations and appointment
OL,9,Frearranged or cancelled as a result.
OL,11,FA strike by consultants and specialist
OL,12,Fdoctors was called off a week before
OL,13,Fit was due to take place.
OL,15,FWhat is on offer?
OL,17,FJunior doctors are being offered a
OL,18,F12.4% uplift for 2023-2024. It
OL,19,Fincludes a 5% paylift which has
OL,20,Falready been paid and will be
OL,21,Fbackdated to April 2023.
