OL,4,Clatest pay deal
OL,6,FA restructure of the pay structure for
OL,7,Fconsultants has been put forward, with
OL,8,Fsome seeing a pay rise of up to 10.1%.
OL,9,FThe aim being to better reward
OL,10,Fperformance and address the gender pay
OL,11,Fgap. It will be backdated to January
OL,12,F2024.
OL,14,FFor specialist doctors, the pay offer
OL,15,Fincludes increases of 6.1%-9.2%, with
OL,16,Fan additional uplift for others.
OL,18,FHow have unions responded?
