OL,3,CDoctors in Wales urged to accept
OL,4,Clatest pay deal
OL,6,FBMA Cymru Wales said the offer has
OL,7,Fbeen reached after weeks of sustained
OL,8,Fpressure and pay negotiations with the
OL,9,FWelsh Government since April.
OL,11,FMembers will have two weeks to vote
OL,12,Fwith the union encouraging doctors to
OL,13,Faccept the offer.
OL,15,FSpeaking on behalf of junior doctors,
OL,16,FDr Oba Babs Osibodu and Dr Peter Fahey
OL,17,Fsaid they are hopeful this step will
OL,18,Fbring them closer to a better future
OL,19,Ffor the profession.
