OL,3,CDoctors in Wales urged to accept
OL,4,Clatest pay deal
OL,6,F"We entered pay negotiations in good
OL,7,Ffaith to reach a deal that will put us
OL,8,Fon the path to achieving full pay
OL,9,Frestoration to address the years of
OL,10,Ferosion to our pay.
OL,12,F"We're satisfied that this offer
OL,13,Fdelivers on our ambition. This offer
OL,14,Fputs us well on the path to pay
OL,15,Frestoration."
OL,17,FAn end to industrial action?
