OL,3,CDoctors in Wales urged to accept
OL,4,Clatest pay deal
OL,6,F"The negotiations have been robust and
OL,7,Fwhile the aim was to end the 2023-24
OL,8,Fdispute and prevent further disruptive
OL,9,Fstrike action, these offers also
OL,10,Fensure the additional investment in
OL,11,Fdoctors' pay is balanced against
OL,12,Fcommitments towards operational
OL,13,Freforms, which seek to address
OL,14,Fproductivity and efficiency and
OL,15,Fachieving future contract reform.
OL,17,F"These pay awards, if accepted, will
OL,18,Falso help to address inequalities in
OL,19,Fthe senior NHS medical workforce."
