OL,3,CDoctors in Wales urged to accept
OL,4,Clatest pay deal
OL,6,FResponding to today's pay offer, the
OL,7,Fleader of the Welsh Conservatives said
OL,8,Fwhilst Labour had dithered, waiting
OL,9,Flists got worse.
OL,11,FAndrew RT Davies said: "After offering
OL,12,Fthe worse settlement figure in the UK
OL,13,Fthe Labour Government claimed there
OL,14,Fwas no money to meet the pay increase.
OL,16,F"Now it appears the money was always
OL,17,Fthere and whilst the Welsh Government
OL,18,Fwere dithering, Wales' longest waiting
OL,19,Flists on record have been exacerbated.
