OL,3,CDoctors in Wales urged to accept
OL,4,Clatest pay deal
OL,6,F"The Welsh Conservatives have been
OL,7,Fclear that we would spend the full
OL,8,FBarnett uplift received for health on
OL,9,Fhealth to end Labour's inhuman two-
OL,10,Fyear waiting lists."
OL,12,FPlaid Cymru spokesperson for Health,
OL,13,FMabon ap Gwynfor MS, said: "We welcome
OL,14,Fthe improved pay offers made to junior
OL,15,Fdoctors, SAS doctors and Consultants,
OL,16,Fand that non-pay elements, such as the
OL,17,Freform of pay scales and contract
OL,18,Fterms will also be included.
