OL,3,CDoctors in Wales urged to accept
OL,4,Clatest pay deal
OL,6,F"Plaid Cymru has been clear: our NHS
OL,7,Fis nothing without its dedicated staff
OL,8,Fand it is only right therefore that
OL,9,Fthey are awarded as such.
OL,11,F"Today's news is a welcome step
OL,12,Fforward. It's now important that
OL,13,Fdiscussions continue and that the
OL,14,FLabour Welsh Government provide a long-
OL,15,Fterm commitment for full pay
OL,16,Frestoration so that hard working NHS
OL,17,Fstaff do not have to consider
OL,18,Findustrial action again."
